'''Bolt tips''' are a [[members]]-only item used to create gem-tipped [[bolts]]. Bolt tips are made through [[Fletching]] skill by cutting [[gem]]s with [[chisel]]. An inventory of 27 gems takes 135 [[tick]]s (81 seconds) to cut into bolt tips.
{{Table/Fletching/Bolt tips}}
Amethyst bolt tips are unique in that they have a [[Crafting]] requirement to make them instead of a Fletching requirement like other bolt tips. These bolt tips may only be attached to [[broad bolts]] to create [[amethyst broad bolts]].
